{"parentUuid":"dfcc10fc-11b6-43ab-822f-b80aa189efc1","isSidechain":false,"message":{"content":[{"text":"几个实用建议：\n\n**1. 精简 CLAUDE.md**\n你的 CLAUDE.md 每次对话都会全量加载。目前内容很详细（战斗流程、架构说明等），可以考虑：\n- 只保留编码规范和构建命令等高频参考信息\n- 把架构文档移到单独文件，需要时再让我读取\n\n**2. 精简 MEMORY.md**\n同理，MEMORY.md 也是每次自动加载的。当前的 Key File Paths 列表很长，可以删减不常用的路径。\n\n**3. 使用更小的模型处理简单任务**\n- `/model` 切换模型 — 简单任务用 Sonnet 或 Haiku，复杂任务再用 Opus\n- 子代理默认也可以用更小的模型\n\n**4. 缩小对话范围**\n- 每个对话聚焦一个任务，完成后开新对话（`/clear` 或新窗口）\n- 避免在一个长对话里做很多不相关的事，上下文越长每次消耗越大\n\n**5. 具体指定文件**\n- 告诉我具体要改哪个文件，而不是让我搜索整个项目\n- 例如\"改 LFPShopWidget.cpp 的 XX 函数\"比\"改商店逻辑\"省很多\n\n**6. 用 .claudeignore**\n在项目根目录创建 `.claudeignore` 文件，排除不需要索引的目录（如 `Binaries/`、`Intermediate/`、`Saved/`、大量 `.uasset` 文件等），减少搜索时的干扰。\n\n要我帮你精简 CLAUDE.md 或 MEMORY.md 吗？","type":"text"}],"id":"msg_01Y3d8Mry9Yzd2kYGBVWqnXj","model":"claude-opus-4-6","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":26939,"output_tokens":574,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"e14a8587-571d-4dfd-be5e-4c5c6afc24b1","timestamp":"2026-04-01T02:11:58.061Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"d:\\UE_Projects\\LFP2D","sessionId":"b4e01b61-dc54-4af5-94ba-2fed1efecdfd","version":"2.1.79","gitBranch":"main"}
