{"parentUuid":"e14a8587-571d-4dfd-be5e-4c5c6afc24b1","isSidechain":false,"promptId":"5beadf61-2d8b-49b8-ad61-ab1fd6bd9766","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<ide_selection>The user selected the lines 58 to 64 from d:\\UE_Projects\\LFP2D\\CLAUDE.md:\nPlayerController::BeginPlay()\r\n  → 绑定 OnPhaseChanged 委托\r\n  → 检测到 BP_Deployment → OnDeploymentPhaseStarted()\r\n    → 高亮出生点、显示布置 UI、玩家放置单位\r\n    → 放置时：按 UnitTypeID/UnitTier 生成单位 → 从 UnitRegistry 初始化属性模板 → 应用已拥有遗物到当前属性\r\n    → 确认 → EndDeploymentPhase() → 注册玩家单位 → BeginNewRound()\r\n\n\nThis may or may not be related to the current task.</ide_selection>"},{"type":"text","text":"你说的“CLAUDE.md 每次对话都会全量加载”，每次对话是指每次新开一组对话，还是每次我问一句话"}]},"uuid":"ff7fd95a-3023-44c7-bbc0-d6a5905fa6c3","timestamp":"2026-04-01T02:16:19.421Z","permissionMode":"default","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"d:\\UE_Projects\\LFP2D","sessionId":"b4e01b61-dc54-4af5-94ba-2fed1efecdfd","version":"2.1.79","gitBranch":"main"}
