{"parentUuid":"e1718597-3ebc-44de-af3a-441b7137b39a","isSidechain":false,"message":{"content":[{"signature":"","thinking":"The user is asking whether CLAUDE.md is loaded \"per conversation\" or \"per message\". Let me clarify this accurately.\n\nIn Claude Code, CLAUDE.md is loaded into the system prompt context. The system prompt is sent with every API call, which means every single message in the conversation. So it's per-message, not just per-conversation.","type":"thinking"}],"id":"msg_01LukAyfSZvYcFwdvxsEEi1Q","model":"claude-opus-4-6","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":777},"cache_creation_input_tokens":777,"cache_read_input_tokens":26922,"input_tokens":3,"output_tokens":9}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"e2b9195a-aac8-4822-ab94-7277cd5e796a","timestamp":"2026-04-01T02:17:59.947Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"d:\\UE_Projects\\LFP2D","sessionId":"b4e01b61-dc54-4af5-94ba-2fed1efecdfd","version":"2.1.79","gitBranch":"main"}
{"parentUuid":"e2b9195a-aac8-4822-ab94-7277cd5e796a","isSidechain":false,"message":{"content":[{"text":"**每次你发一句话（每条消息）都会加载。**\n\nCLAUDE.md 和 MEMORY.md 是作为系统提示的一部分发送的，每次 API 调用都会携带。也就是说你在一个对话里问 10 个问题，这些内容就被发送了 10 次。\n\n所以精简它们的收益是乘数级的 — 减少 1000 token 的内容，10 轮对话就省了 10000 input tokens。\n\n要我帮你精简吗？比如把战斗流程那段（你选中的部分）和架构详述移到单独文件，CLAUDE.md 只留核心规范。","type":"text"}],"id":"msg_01LukAyfSZvYcFwdvxsEEi1Q","model":"claude-opus-4-6","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":777,"cache_read_input_tokens":26922,"output_tokens":288,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":777},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"284d9050-2e55-44b3-a5a0-03f2427876b0","timestamp":"2026-04-01T02:17:59.968Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"d:\\UE_Projects\\LFP2D","sessionId":"b4e01b61-dc54-4af5-94ba-2fed1efecdfd","version":"2.1.79","gitBranch":"main"}
