{"parentUuid":"e4d183d8-a341-4522-b217-ea82195aadb0","isSidechain":false,"message":{"content":[{"text":"对，对话越长消耗越大，因为每次发消息都要把**整个对话历史**发给 API。\n\n**Compact（`/compact`）有用**，它会把之前的对话压缩成摘要，大幅减少上下文长度。适合在对话中途、完成一个阶段后执行。\n\n**消耗模型大致是：**\n```\n每条消息成本 = 系统提示(CLAUDE.md等) + 对话历史 + 当前消息\n```\n\n所以省 token 的优先级：\n1. **精简 CLAUDE.md / MEMORY.md** — 每条消息都省，乘数效应最大\n2. **及时 `/compact`** — 压缩对话历史\n3. **早点开新对话** — 彻底清空历史\n4. **简单任务用小模型** — `/model` 切 Sonnet\n\n要我现在帮你精简 CLAUDE.md 和 MEMORY.md？预计能减掉一半以上内容。","type":"text"}],"id":"msg_01Wfh3Sse8WZe9vfnUCQfv63","model":"claude-opus-4-6","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":9846,"cache_read_input_tokens":18132,"output_tokens":326,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":9846},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"0d8026dd-cb43-4404-bd65-85c5412f3dc6","timestamp":"2026-04-01T03:00:02.039Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"d:\\UE_Projects\\LFP2D","sessionId":"b4e01b61-dc54-4af5-94ba-2fed1efecdfd","version":"2.1.79","gitBranch":"main"}
